text:
Meet Oregon's high school football all-stars: Les Schwab Bowl 2017 North roster Updated February 21, 2017 Comment LES SCHWAB BOWL 2017 - NORTH ROSTER 
The 2017 Les Schwab Bowl -- an annual all-star football game featuring many of the state's top graduated seniors -- will take place June 24 at Hillsboro Stadium. 
Here's a look at the players selected for the North roster. Check back later this week to meet the South all-stars. RUNNING BACKS & DEFENSIVE BACKS
